messages.message:
Hey team, wanted to confirm a behaviour I notice on instabase.com (http://instabase.com).

When we haven’t logged in to instabase.com (http://instabase.com), and try to access our spaces (eg. https://instabase.com/saikat_biswas) it shows the error `No subspaces to show`. I had expected to see the login prompt.

Is this expected? This can enable public users to figure out the user names without having access to ib.com (http://ib.com).

Please let me know if this is not the right channel for this, I’ll move it there.
